quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,61,"And when the two companies saw one another, the companions of Moses said, "
  26,62,"[Moses] said, "
  26,63,"Then We inspired to Moses, "
  27,34,"She said, "
  27,35,"But indeed, I will send to them a gift and see with what [reply] the messengers will return."
  27,36,"So when they came to Solomon, he said, "
  28,7,"And We inspired to the mother of Moses, "
  28,8,"And the family of Pharaoh picked him up [out of the river] so that he would become to them an enemy and a [cause of] grief. Indeed, Pharaoh and Hāmān and their soldiers were deliberate sinners."
  28,9,"And the wife of Pharaoh said, ",footnotes:1:[What would be the result of that.]
